events.description:
The in-person Entrepreneurship Simulation Game is one December 8th in the Lower Cafe, starting at 6:00 PM. Seats are limited.

Investor – decide which startup(s) to back
Founder – pitch, recruit, and build your dream team
Employee – find the company that’s the best match for you

This holiday season, don’t just give back—strategize! Discover how purpose and profit can go hand in hand with this timely session on Corporate Social Responsibility (CSR) for small and mid-size companies. 
Learn at Launch: Purpose & Profit offers practical, non-fluffy strategies for weaving social responsibility and community impact into your everyday business opera
